{
  "stem": "13063.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's called in German, [GERMAN], meaning the soup had everything-- meat, whatever meat they had-- horse meat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever was in-- in that bowl of soup that people who did not observe Kashrut ate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those who did observe Kashrut had to bring their own food from home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the ghetto--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly schlepping things, carrying heavy loads, stones, pails of-- of-- of-- hay, you know, compressed hay, all kinds of-- all kinds of work, and-- and building roads and-- and-- and carrying wood.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, menial work, menial work, physical work, all physical work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same thing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was also taken, mostly with me, see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we worked together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The women were-- were taken to shovel snow, see, from the ghetto-- to shovel snow, and to-- they were returned to the ghetto later in the evening, like we, together.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] coming back home, we were so exhausted that all we can do-- all we could do was just collapse and have some few hours of sleep.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We tried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tried to hide on Shabbat in order not to be taken to-- by the Germans to-- to their forced labor outposts.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Shabbat-- what can you-- as-- as-- as I said before, we had services at the rabbi's on Shabbat in the ghetto, and most of the time, most of the time, I did not have to work on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just did all kinds of-- of-- of acrobatics not to-- not to be-- not to have to go out and work on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know that I-- we bribed somebody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They should go for health.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We bribed the Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans were very amenable to bribes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were some-- you know, some Germans who could be bribed and-- let him go.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
